{"tid":1304942,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"示威者應該走向兩極化","createTime":"2019-07-10T17:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T18:31:31.000Z","uid":174301,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7dbe05e1ddebb934ce41a95cb8a32df0fd6b13e","tid":1304942,"uid":174301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:42:45.000Z","msg":"和理派繼續和理 前線繼續前線<br />\n<br />\n是但一方失利，應該立即轉陣。文宣比人打，勇武前來支援; 前線受困，文宣落場助陣。<br />\n<br />\n兩方俱受圍困則各司天命，相信自己既直覺，想做就做，好過坐係屋企等赤化。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請記返起97年前香港人的光輝</span><br />\n<br />\n歷史話比我地知，中間派已經無用。政府太易預測，反而極端的事情對面極小去防範及分析，例如TVB 的事再比到相關組織應有既壓力，我諗TVB 自己都無諗過香港人咁絕情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之，<span style=\"color: red;\">想做就去做</span>，出奇不意，走向極端化。<br />\n<br />\n夢到神的啟示，整合晒比大家睇，soryy for 1999"},{"pid":"4b8cbc49b39390e32851a6b087f049ec2f255d28","tid":1304942,"uid":107216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:44:20.000Z","msg":"不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75aa71b1d3f78fa1bce883bd4a91b3a20e1f9b7","tid":1304942,"uid":92230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:50:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n遊行 -&gt; 死線 -&gt; 勇武</span></span>"},{"pid":"afb856d726d546ed635d48764a075f5b27e9e2c4","tid":1304942,"uid":174301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d75aa71b1d3f78fa1bce883bd4a91b3a20e1f9b7","tid":1304942,"uid":92230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:50:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n遊行 -&gt; 死線 -&gt; 勇武</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:54:01.000Z","msg":"做咩都好，錯左仲有手足補上。<br />\n<br />\n用試錯法，一直搵到出路。<br />\n<br />\n二百萬人 一即是全 全即是一"},{"pid":"1557c6e182fc3d9aba6132d6b1f3